Hey guys  Also make sure the cotter pins are in the axle nuts and lug nuts 
tight    I towed a splittie that had loose lug nuts and almost lost a wheel had 
to rob some lugs off the other whells, also didnt have the cotter pins and 
axle nuts started to come off that would have been a bitch   used the antenna  as 
a cotter pin  later and have fun  Mark Dearing
